{{Quote|Offworld smuggling of rock ivory is reaching crisis proportions. At this rate we won't have enough ivory to repair our own repulsorlift engines. I am authorized to offer you a substantial reward for reconnaissance of the main smuggling gang's location.|An individual offering a recon mission to a spacer|<ref name="SWG:PRI">{{SWGcite|exp=AED|type=terminal|Explorer|Precious Rock Ivory}}</ref>}}
'''Rock ivory''' was a valuable substance used for [[Repulsorlift/Legends|anti-gravity]] generators. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] once smuggled 100 [[Kilogram/Legends|kilos]] of it for [[Grambo]].

